snippet.title: Marvel’s Spider-Man - Silver Lining: DLC 3 Teaser | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/marvels-spider-man/?emcid=or-1s-412983

In the tension-filled finale to Marvel’s Spider-Man: The City That Never Sleeps, the web-slinger must rely on unlikely allies to protect the city from calamity. 

Marvel's Spider-Man: Silver Lining is available for download on the PlayStation®4 system December 21, 2018. 

Marvel’s Spider-Man: The City That Never Sleeps is downloadable content for Marvel’s Spider-Man; may be sold separately. Marvel’s Spider-Man required to play associated downloadable content. Footage from Marvel’s Spider-Man: Silver Lining shown.
